<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A6304014001">
<title>
DTC Detecting Condition and Trouble Area
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.347in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.778in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
C1153: Power Supply Voltage too Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured voltage of fail-safe relay contact is lower than 9 V even if engine speed is more than 600 rpm and commanded fail-safe relay ON.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Charging system
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
P/S control module
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
C1155: P/S Control Module Internal Failure / Power Supply Voltage too High
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
P/S control module is internally faulty or measured voltage of fail-safe relay contact is too high.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
